{"title":"观海","authors":["胡世宗"],"dates":[{"year":1990,"month":3,"day":6}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"观海"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"胡世宗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"１"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每天每天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我都要去海边，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"重温那两个字："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浩……瀚。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"２"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"涌动的海面，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是鸥鸟的停机坪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从这里起飞的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都怀有无畏的魂灵。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"３"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"海是情感的调解盘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无论是憎是爱，是悲是欢，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都可以成为知心朋友，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只要你站到她跟前。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"４"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"海不是轻浮的小生，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不像湖水常把树林飞鸟倒映；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只有壮丽的旭日初升，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"才让肩头披上彤红的斗篷。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"５"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁曾见过，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"整个海洋结为坚冰一块？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"结冰的大都不是海，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"即使在数九寒天。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"６"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"海很温柔，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当她亲切地抚慰地球；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"海又十分威严，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当她暴怒地反抗宇宙。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"７"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有涨潮就有落潮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"落潮时不必心焦；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"涨潮的时刻，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还会来到！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"８"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有时海面上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"免不了也飘着油污、朽叶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可谁能因此否认"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大海的纯洁？！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"９"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一切都考验过了："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"炸雷、暴雨、巨风，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都撼不动"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"海燕对海的忠诚！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}